Averages from included subjects (n=22; from the nonRQ analysis)¶

  • Mean target proportion: 44.8% (SEM: 5.4%)
  • Mean random guess: 55.1% (SEM: 5.4%)
  • Mean SD: 30.5 deg (SEM: 5.4 deg)
